name: Simpsons Guest Stars
content:
Description: data about guest stars on The Simpsons, seasons 1-30.

[Source](https://github.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/tree/master/data/2019/2019-08-27)

Columns:

* Season (numerical): what season a given episode was aired during
* Number (string): production number for that episode
* Production code (string): TV production code for that episode
* Episode Title (string): name of Simpsons episode
* Guest Star (string): name of the guest star for that episode
* Role (string): name of the character/role the guest star played, such as "Themselves" or a fictional role
